Here's a look at the current Covid-19 trends in Africa: Less than 1 per cent of Kenyans reported adverse reactions, State says. Both infectious disease units at the Kenyatta National Hospital and Mbagathi Hospital are almost full. Detectives are still trying to unravel how and where Owino acquired weapon handling skills. Since the election of Magufuli as President in 2015, Tanzania’s human rights record had deteriorated. In September 2018, he denounced family planning and asked women to shun contraceptives.